front.title: •Hermi Odle
front.gametext: When in a battle, you may 'react' by deploying any one non-unique blaster (for free) on Hermi from Reserve Deck. reshuffle. When present with your Advosze at a site, allows your character weapons to transfer for free there.
front.lore: Baragwin assigned by Jabba to be the palace's master weaponsmith. Enemy of Pote Snitkin.
